# Client browser verification

Before marking Phase 7 or 8 done in PLAN.md, run the multi-tab flows in [docs/browser-testing.md](../../docs/browser-testing.md).

- One dev stack: `npm run dev` → client `:5173`, server `:3001`
- Poll until **`Connection: open`** before create/join
- Multi-tab players: `localStorage.setItem('dice:name', '<name>')` per tab; rejoin uses stored `playerName`
- See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the agent checklist
